page.title: 11 North Cove
page.content: North Cove has a very big playing field and it has got a seesaw,swings and BMX track plus a climbing frame made of logs.Kids go down there and it's one of the main attraction's in North Cove. We also have a little shop which is quiet useful when you've run out of things.North Cove and Barnby have guides and brownies.They meet at the hall.Guides is on Tuesday and Brownies is on Thursday.In North Cove there are lots of new detached houses in one long cul-desac called Pinewood Gardens.There are about 501 people living in North Cove.North Cove church has some paintings which are being restoed.North Cove is a lovely village.
